{"id":847809738,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"5 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1669089757,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"37 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/847809738/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Perfect Squares","memory":"41.7 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int numSquares(int n) {\n        int dp[]=new int[n+1];\n        Arrays.fill(dp,n);\n        dp[0]=0;\n        for(int i=0;i<n+1;i++){\n            for(int j=1;j<i+1;j++){\n                int square=j*j;\n                if(i-square<0){\n                    break;\n                }else{\n                    dp[i]=Math.min(dp[i],1+dp[i-square]);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return dp[n];\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"perfect-squares","has_notes":false}
